#: ../../../userspace-api/media/v4l/dev-sdr.rst:92
msgid ""
"The data format or type of compression, set by the application. This is a "
"little endian :ref:`four character code <v4l2-fourcc>`. V4L2 defines SDR "
"formats in :ref:`sdr-formats`."
msgstr ""

